Codes are available in readme.md file.
Jupyter Notebook or any online python compiler can be used for execution.
You can download the dataset "AllProductReviews.csv" available in the repository.
In the code,commands are already given for importing and downoading  the libraries required for the program. 
Change the location of the file for "loading csv file" as your downloaded csv file location.
Execute the code,enter the input for required product available in the dataset.
You will get top 10 positive and negative reviews for the desired product.
